**Task**: Fix failing test DBB-010 (`await Promise.resolve(42)` in `executeCode()`)

**Root cause**: `quickjs-emscripten`'s `evalCode()` doesn't support top-level `await`.

**Fix** (`src/tools/code.ts`):
- When code contains `await`, use `newAsyncContext()` instead of `getQuickJS().newContext()`
- Wrap the code in an async IIFE and capture result/error in QuickJS globals
- Call `vm.runtime.executePendingJobs()` to flush the microtask queue
- Read `__asyncResult` / `__asyncError` from the global scope

**Result**: All 25 tests pass, task moved to `review`.
